<a href="/wol/rslink/r7/lp-j?lang=J&amp;docid=502016235&amp;pub=ijwyp"><img src="/ja/wol/mp/r7/lp-j/lff/2021/1424" data-img-small-src="/ja/wol/mp/r7/lp-j/lff/2021/1423" alt="" width="1200" height="675" class="suppressZoom" /></a>
</figure>
</div>
<div id="tt87" class="dc-column-width--threeQuarters du-margin-children-vertical--0">
<p id="p51" data-pid="51">聖書は，同性愛者を憎むように勧めているのでしょうか。</p>
<p id="p52" data-pid="52"><a href="/ja/wol/pc/r7/lp-j/1102021241/1/0"><strong>「同性愛は間違っていますか」</strong>（jw.orgの記事）</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="tt88" class="dc-columns-desktopOnly du-borderStyle-top--solid du-borderColor--gray-100 du-borderWidth--1 du-margin-top--4 du-margin-bottom-mobileOnly--6 du-padding-top--4">
<div id="f9" class="dc-column-width--oneQuarter du-margin-inlineEnd-desktopOnly--4 du-margin-bottom-mobileOnly--4">
